#C  IsCopyable( <obj> ) . . . . . . . . . . . . test if an object is copyable
##
##  <#GAPDoc Label="IsCopyable">
##  <ManSection>
##  <Filt Name="IsCopyable" Arg='obj' Type='Category'/>
##
##  <Description>
##  If a mutable form of an object <A>obj</A> can be made in &GAP;,
